headline: How The Story For Marathon Petroleum (MPC) Is Shifting As Analyst Views Diverge
summary: Analysts have been shifting their price targets for Marathon Petroleum, with some lifting estimates by up to US$28 while others are trimming them by as much as US$47. These changes reflect very different views on refining fundamentals, earnings power into 2026 and how much investors may be willing to pay on a P/E basis.
